{"tid":476729,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢老互劈】廣源邨2長者噪音問題嘈　七旬翁遭捅斃","createTime":"2017-11-22T09:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T01:32:33.000Z","uid":37661,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7cf7d206277b6654c7a93b680f7f39601b8e8757","tid":476729,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:18:57.000Z","msg":"廣源邨2長者噪音問題嘈　七旬翁遭捅斃<br />\n<br />\n沙田發生兇殺案！下午3時許，一名姓潘(73歲)老翁，與一名姓黎(77歲)老翁，在廣源邨商場對開露天空地，疑因噪音問題發生爭執，繼而扭作一團在花槽糾纏，保安員見狀，即時上前將2人分開，期間赫見潘翁胸口及腹部淌血，有人手持一把利刀，隨即報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n大批警員接報趕至，當時潘翁已經昏迷，救護員即場替其急救後，再由救護車送院搶救，惟最終因傷重不治；黎翁亦受傷需送院治理。警方封鎖現場調查，現場遺下染血衣服、啤酒、銀包、手機、以及香煙和鞋等物件。據悉，2名老翁同住廣源邨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171122/photo/bkn-20171122155917237-1122_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171122170643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171122%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171122155917237-1122_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171122170643&h=ad12c256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171122/bkn-20171122155917237-1122_00822_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171122%2Fbkn-20171122155917237-1122_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=zHqKsc4XsIYGQJODhmHhQ5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=35e6586a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171122/bkn-20171122155917237-1122_00822_001.html?refer=hn</a>"},{"pid":"ed050f738bc514cace258ef41f45c6b96d2f37a3","tid":476729,"uid":29128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be95dfaaebdae4c511393c97ff044e4427f21d6","tid":476729,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:37:20.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/no